, X., Sánchez, A., Ammonia emissions from the composting of different organic wastes. Dependency on process temperature (2006) Chemosphere, 62 (9), pp. 1534-1542; Peregrina, C.A., Lecomte, D., Arlabosse, P., Rudolph, V., Life Cycle Assessment (LCA) applied to the design of an innovative drying process for sewage sludge (2006) Process Safety and Environmental Protection, 84, pp. 270-279; Peruzzi, E., Macci, C., Doni, S., Masciandaro, G., Peruzzi, P., Aiello, M., Caccianti, B., Wetland cane (Phragmites australis) for sewage sludge stabilization (2007) Proceedings of the International Conference on Multi Functions of Wetland Systems, Padova, Italy, , M. Borin, S. Bacelle (Eds.); Ponsá, S., Gea, T., Alerm, L., Cerezo, J., Sánchez, A., Comparison of aerobic and anaerobic stability indices through a MSW biological treatment process (2008) Waste Management, 28 (12), pp. 2735-2742; Sarkar, U., Hobbs, S.E., Landfill odour: assessment of emissions by the flux footprint method (2003) Environmental Modelling & Software, 18 (2), pp. 155-163; Scaglia, B., Adani, F., An index for quantifying the aerobic reactivity of municipal solid wastes and derived waste products (2008) Science of the Total Environment, 394, pp. 183-191; Singh, R.P., Agrawal, M., Potential benefits and risks of land application of sewage sludge (2008) Waste Management, 28, pp. 347-358; Suh, Y., Rousseaux, P., An LCA of alternative wastewater sludge treatment scenarios (2002) Resources, Conservation and Recycling, 35, pp. 191-200; Svantröm, M., Fröling, M., Modell, M., Peters, W.A., Tester, J., Environmental assessment of supercritical water oxidation of sewage sludge (2004) Resources, Conservation and Recycling, 41, pp. 321-338; Tarantini, M., Buttol, P., Maiorino, L., An environmental LCA of alternative scenarios of urban sewage sludge treatment and disposal (2007) Thermal Science, 3, pp. 153-164; Uggetti, E., Llorens, E., Pedescoll, A., Ferrer, I., Castellnou, R., García, J., Sludge dewatering and stabilisati